abstract: PARIS -- The most interesting development in political Europe today is the disappearance of dogma. Nations deal increasingly in terms of pragmatic self-interest without regard to ideological theory.

WEST POINT, N. Y., Oct. 28 -- Ken Wyrick and Joe Neuman, Army's defensive tackles, did an excellent job rushing and penetrating Boston College's offense last Saturday. Theirs was just part of a strong defensive performance that unbalanced the Eagles and helped the Cadets gain a 38-7 victory.
